snippet.title: DemonCrawl - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
DemonCrawl is a puzzle roguelite that combines the addicting gameplay of Minesweeper with hundreds of unique items, stages, and abilities!

Available for PC and Android on November 5th, 2019.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1141220/DemonCrawl/
Gameplay trailer: https://youtu.be/M3TJgSNcYIU


Music - "The Big Conference" by DJ Williams.
